{"id": 2136, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得有益的争论应该满足那些标准？", "description": "认真你才不会输。", "record_count": 10118, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180123112706BX2OEmPdpVLtT6a0.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-23T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3616, "title": "你觉得有益的争论应该满足那些标准？", "content": "你觉得有益的争论应该满足那些标准？ ", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 261031, "content": "把争论定义为辩论，而不是冲突 ", "image": "img/option/option/20180123150951sH4Xnbk8S73FhqLM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261030, "content": "不否认对方的对话资格", "image": "img/option/option/20180123150942w8XAPd59sBWtln3M.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261034, "content": "争论时假设自己是对的，倾听时假设自己是错的", "image": "img/option/option/20180123151003x3EcVzqs8IK7P1rY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261037, "content": "复述对方观点时有敬意，而不是断章取义并反击", "image": "img/option/option/201801231455476bp1FwnjxgBaImer.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261038, "content": "承认自己和批评者意见一致的方面", "image": "img/option/option/201801231510248gBOmvnTJ42LDudr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261039, "content": "边讨论边完善自己的观点，努力把想法表达明确", "image": "img/option/option/20180123151040nlS7mTRXgjrG4EcC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261040, "content": "只要拿得出有力的论据，允许对方改变你的想法", "image": "img/option/option/20180123151052hZYN8qAvesko4E92.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 261041, "content": "不必以说服对方为结束，能加深自己的认识就很好", "image": "img/option/option/20180123152402gfPwk3SrldmXs2ne.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}